### § 2a. SQLite Database (`server/db/`)

**All 30+ server modules** now use SQLite via `better-sqlite3` (all 5 migration PRs merged).

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `db/index.ts` | DB singleton, WAL mode, foreign keys ON, migration runner |
| `db/migrate-json.ts` | One-time JSON→SQLite migration script (`npx tsx server/db/migrate-json.ts`), idempotent via INSERT OR IGNORE |
| `db/migrations/001-payments.sql` | `payments` table |
| `db/migrations/002-global-singletons.sql` | `users`, `client_users`, `reset_tokens`, `activity_log`, `requests`, `churn_signals`, `anomalies`, `audit_schedules` |
| `db/migrations/003-per-workspace.sql` | `approval_batches`, `content_briefs`, `content_topic_requests`, `content_posts`, `work_orders`, `recommendation_sets`, `annotations`, `seo_changes`, `decay_analyses`, `roi_snapshots`, `feedback`, `rank_tracking_config`, `rank_snapshots` |
| `db/migrations/004-per-site-and-config.sql` | `audit_snapshots`, `schema_snapshots`, `redirect_snapshots`, `performance_snapshots`, `chat_sessions`, `google_tokens`, `usage_tracking` |
| `db/migrations/005-workspaces.sql` | `workspaces` (30+ columns), `page_edit_states`, `seo_edit_tracking` |

**Key patterns (follow these when writing new DB code):**
- **Lazy prepared statements:** `let _stmt: ... | null = null;` cached at module level
- **JSON columns:** Arrays/objects stored as `TEXT`, parsed at read boundary
- **Row→Model mappers:** `rowToX()` functions convert snake_case DB rows → camelCase TS interfaces
- **Three-state booleans:** SQLite `INTEGER` (0/1/NULL) → `boolean | undefined` for workspace toggles
- **Migration tracking:** `_migrations` table tracks applied `.sql` files; new migrations go in `server/db/migrations/`

